      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so i checked under the sink and i think i have a wrench and a screwdriver but i'm not sure what kind of washers i need. do i just buy a random pack or is there a specific way to know? also is it hard to get the old stuff out without breaking the pipe?",
